{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act46side", "eventName": "雪山降臨1101", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OS-1", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "呼號聲中", "storyInfo": "天災發生後，三大家族立刻開始了救援工作。但是天災帶來的恐慌還是在人群中蔓延開來。就在這個時候，恩雅發現雅兒失蹤了。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G1_stationruins", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crowdtalk_fear", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.8, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一隊，把物資放到東邊的空地。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "配合佩爾羅契的增援一起搭建醫療帳篷，準備接收傷患！", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞭解！", "name": "救援隊員A"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二隊，帶上雪鏟和酒袋，繼續在火車站那邊的廢墟尋找倖存者。仔細搜，不要漏聽呼救聲。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明白！各位，帶上東西跟我走——", "name": "救援隊員B"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "切記不要發出太大的聲音，山上的情況還不清楚，不排除還有發生二次雪崩的可能。探查情況的小隊已經在去往山頂的路上了。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相信我們的同伴，相信耶拉岡德正在庇佑著謝拉格人。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#3$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德在上。", "name": "救援隊員B"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……耶拉岡德在上。", "name": "救援隊員A"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德在上。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時間不等人，立刻開始行動吧。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是！", "name": "眾救援隊員"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowcrwdmarch", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "交疊在一起的回答聲還未從冷風中散去，希瓦艾什家的侍從已經在雪地上散開，奔向各個方向。"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡的不只有他們，這場白色的崩潰顯然在祥和的日子裡造成了一片清晰的創口。"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G1_stationruins", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowfall", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡！這裡還有一個活著的！", "name": "救援隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂——撐住啊！是個謝拉格人就給我咬牙撐住，別睡著！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "腿，我的腿……", "name": "受傷的男人"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的腿動不了，我的腿已經……呃！", "name": "受傷的男人"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別動！後面的，情況看清楚了沒？到底怎麼樣？！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "挖開了，雪洞已經挖開了！但是他的腿被鋼筋壓住了，如果這根東西沒斷就只能找醫生來……不對，先別急，我再挖開一點試試看！", "name": "救援隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_brnchflsnw", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——嘿！呼……好消息，這根鋼筋已經完全斷了，我們只要能抬起來就好了！", "name": "救援隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出力氣能辦好的事都不用擔心，都過來，幫個忙！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "阿克托斯", "content": "抓穩了，一、二、三！"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_scratchmetalwall", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "sc"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sc", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 12.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "阿克托斯", "content": "——喝啊！"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "痛、呃啊啊……好痛……", "name": "受傷的男人"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，稍微抬起來了，把他拖出來！儘快！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我拉住他了，輕一點，把他的身體抬起來，用布墊在底下，對，小心，別扯到他的傷口……", "name": "救援隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_283_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "救援隊員", "content": "就這樣慢慢地拖出來——"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothtrailground", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "救援隊員", "content": "好！成功了！擔架，快點把擔架拿過來！"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_kneelsnow_s", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "借過一下，借過一下，擔架來了！", "name": "羅德島醫療幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "壓抑著的、克制著的呼喚。救援。擔架。生還者。"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白茫茫的雪地之上，無數人忙碌地奔跑著，臉頰滾燙，甚至溢出汗水。"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古羅，這邊暫時交給你。看好了，能救活的一個也別放棄。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_260_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "古羅", "content": "瞭解！"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_260_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "古羅", "content": "但……您要去哪裡？"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G1_stationruins", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿克托斯老爺……南側的救援難道已經結束了？", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#4$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒，還沒結束。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古羅在看著，我是來找你的。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這裡還算順利，您不用擔心。布朗陶的增援也到了，帶來了不少毛毯和食物。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菈塔托絲夫人本想親自過來的，但似乎實在是抽不出身。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……算了，想想也是。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家心裡有數，沒有人會因為這個怪她的。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*謝拉格俚語*，怎麼會碰上這場災難！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次雪崩來得太突然了，沒有一點徵兆，我們所有人都沒有準備。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#6$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，就是這個，我要找你說的就是這件事！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道謝拉格的規矩，這場雪崩發生的地方在佩爾羅契家的領地，我們負責照看領地內的雪山。", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們一直在記錄積雪的厚度，那個記錄我看了好幾次，明明一切正常！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#7$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我才來問你，你們那個什麼研究院裡不是還有人專門跑去看雪山的嗎？那些人怎麼說？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "研究院……您說萊茵生命？", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#4$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，他們天天在山上跑來跑去的，安裝那些高科技裝備，總不能一點發現都沒有吧？", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_199_yak_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按理來說應該是有的。但他們也有自己的任務，未必會把所有精力都放在研究雪山上。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#2$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且雪崩發生後我們立刻就趕過來了，他們到底有沒有發現什麼，我也不是很確定。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#2$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯老爺也派了鐧小姐帶領隊伍上山調查，應該很快就能回來了。", "name": "角峰"}, "figure_art": "avg_199_yak_1#2$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#2$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，總覺得有點毛骨悚然，這場雪崩到底是什麼鬼……", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#9$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "s"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "s", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "山風夾雜著雪花，呼嘯而來。小山一般高大的男人回頭，他站在山腳下，在沉默的山峰前他就如同一顆小石頭。"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "s", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是……", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#4$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跌落的雪鋪成一片白色，一行人正從山路上快速下撤。幾步就到了二人附近。"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowrun", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "b", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "角峰大人！", "name": "調查隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們得儘快通知恩希歐迪斯老爺！山、山上發現——", "name": "調查隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "調查隊員臉色發白，他的毛靴底部，被踩汙的雪凝成一片濕潤而冰冷的灰色。"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為奔跑而急促的呼吸夾雜在風中，凝聚成一股令人不安的嗚咽。"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於框架協議，各位代表沒有別的問題了，那麼我們接下來開始討論協議細則。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "首先是第一項，關於謝拉格與卡西米爾的聯合礦場的稅務——", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）董事長，鐧小姐有要事回報，正在門外等待。", "name": "喀蘭貿易職員"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……現在？", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）是，她說……非常緊急。", "name": "喀蘭貿易職員"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "45_g11_karlanheadquarters", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊急的事？", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "調查隊在雪崩發生處的山上發現了這個。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐧伸出手，她戴著手套，一小片漆黑的源石碎片靜靜地躺在她的手中。"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……在謝拉格的山上？", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#4$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果火車站旁邊的那座雪山還算謝拉格境內的話，沒錯。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾希斯和羅德島的人都看過了，基本可以確定……", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐧環顧四周，確定沒有第三個人後，才壓低聲音說道。"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場雪崩，就是天災。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有多少人知道？", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "調查隊是我們的人，姑且還能控制，但是山下已經發現了不少感染的人。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "消息瞞不住太久。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通知角峰，立刻封鎖受災現場，不要讓運送貨物的民眾靠近。山上也要設置管制點。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聯絡羅德島，請他們在收治感染者時一定要注意保密，需要什麼幫助都可以聯絡喀蘭貿易。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再幫我轉告菈塔托絲和阿克托斯，一個小時後在受災的火車站見面，請他們務必要趕到。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。還有別的嗎？", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你帶著足夠的人手，立刻去蔓珠院。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同樣……讓諾希斯帶人，去保護萊茵生命觀測站。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞭解。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯整理了一下衣裝，轉身走進了會議室。"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉各位，耽誤了一點時間，讓我們繼續吧。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "首先是第一項，關於謝拉格與卡西米爾的聯合礦場的稅務……", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g3_mainhall", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "荒唐……荒唐！", "name": "年長的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有的典籍都未記載過這樣的預言。耶拉岡德怎麼會用天災來懲罰我們？這根本就是無稽之談！", "name": "年長的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但天災已經發生了！祂已經因為憤怒，離我們而去了！", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不是耶拉岡德的怒火，我們又要如何解釋現在發生的這場天災？", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看此時此刻圍在蔓珠院外的人們吧，他們都是耶拉岡德虔誠的信徒，是謝拉格善良的子民。", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道我們要告訴他們，你們失去的親人、你們遭受的苦難……全都是無妄之災？", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今人心已經亂作一團，動搖信仰的聲音不絕於耳……然而越是如此，我們的信念越是要堅定。", "name": "年長的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們怎知這不是耶拉岡德施予我們的考驗，只是讓我們信念堅定的考驗？", "name": "年長的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶拉岡德沒有捨棄謝拉格……耶拉岡德怎會無故懲罰謝拉格？", "name": "年長的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道不是我們做了忤逆耶拉岡德的事，才會——", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年輕修士看了看坐在大殿中央的聖女，又悻悻低下頭去，一言不發。"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必顧慮，暢所欲言即可。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女大人……", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我認為，這是耶拉岡德的怒火，這是……這是警示……", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許正是因為蔓珠院……因為我們做了錯的決定。", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許我們就不該同意那些無信仰之人在聖山上大興土木，我們應該堅持，堅持拒絕……", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不是那些人褻瀆了耶拉岡德的聖殿——使祂發怒，謝拉格又怎麼會……", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的聲音越來越低，聲音中的顫抖卻越來越微弱。整座大殿也跟著安靜下來，無人出聲反駁。"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白了。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您認為，是我作為聖女做出了冒犯耶拉岡德的決定，如今才為謝拉格招致了這場天災。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不、不是……聖女大人，我的意思是……", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，你的觀點很有參考意義——如今不只是山下的信眾，還有和我一同坐在這裡的諸位，其中應該有不少人都懷抱著與你一樣的想法。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是如今的情況，人們對蔓珠院產生懷疑，而各位也心懷忐忑與搖擺。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "方戈修士還有羅納亞修士，你們一個認為耶拉岡德仍如舊日般眷顧我們，神恩永濟；而另一個則認為耶拉岡德已然……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少女垂下頭思考片刻。潔白的臉上幾乎如同冰面一般平靜。"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就請兩位向我背誦，《耶拉岡德》中提及的三次“守護”吧。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是，聖女大人。", "name": "兩位修士"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第一處守護，《耶拉岡德》，第七頁第九行。", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“於是祂對身邊的牧童說——”", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我將是你們的庇佑，我將是你們的依靠。”", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我會在林中狩獵，我將在土地中播種，讓你們有皮毛穿、有東西吃，不至於凍死與餓死。”", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“這正是祂守護我們不被寒風與飢腸轆轆侵害的時候。”", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_268", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第二處守護，《耶拉岡德》，第二十五頁第十七行。", "name": "年長的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“所以守護者在人群中誕生了，他們在七彩的雲霞之中甦醒，以雪水澆灌的泥土構建高牆。”", "name": "年長的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“這正是祂守護我們的家宅與親眷的時刻，賜予我們抵禦外來之敵的技巧。”", "name": "年長的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_268"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及……《耶拉岡德》，第三十九頁第二行。最後一處提及。", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“那一日，祂在人群之中宣講。”", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我的眼睛會看護你們，我的皮毛會溫暖你們，我的脊骨會守護你們，我的血肉將成為對你們的賜福。”", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“你們已經知曉風雪的道理，瞭解行走的姿態。”", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“你們已是謝拉格的謝拉格人，這謝拉格的土地從此徹徹底底地……交到了謝拉格人的手上。”", "name": "激動的修士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2014_1#1$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼請各位回答我，《耶拉岡德》是否有任何一句提及，耶拉岡德會保護謝拉格永遠不受天災侵害嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道各位，是在代替耶拉岡德向祂的子民許諾嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#8$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "滿座之中，不少修士低下頭去不再言語。"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寂靜得落針可聞。焚香的氣息縈繞在每一個人鼻尖，卻讓他們覺得連呼吸都凝滯在如今的談話中。"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……聖女大人，言之有理。", "name": "蔓珠院長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#7$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天災降臨在了謝拉格，有人因此而死，更多人因此染病。", "name": "蔓珠院長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今這個消息已經傳遍了整個雪境。恐懼、不安、進一步的悲傷甚至憤怒，這些東西正在謝拉格人身上流淌。", "name": "蔓珠院長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們要做的是為此尋找解決之法。", "name": "蔓珠院長老"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是自然。現在不是我們爭辯的時候。我所說的這些話也正是為了警示各位，不可陷入慌亂與偏執。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在座的各位，都是耶拉岡德的信徒，應當知曉言語的分量。從現在開始，蔓珠院眾人不得再妄言耶拉岡德的懲罰。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從明天開始，我會進入藏經閣，全心解經，傾聽祂的聲音。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿德頌長老。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在。", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#1$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在你已經接任大長老之位，我閉關期間，蔓珠院事務一應由你代理。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安撫信眾、舉行悼喪儀式、抄寫賑災慰靈的經文，一應事務不可遺漏。都要盡心盡力，誠懇而行。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1998_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是……", "name": "阿德頌"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1998_1#7$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們應該相信……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……謝拉格曾經經歷過無數風雪與難關，蔓珠院會永遠與耶拉岡德的子民同在。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g4_boudoir", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#3$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好，總算沒出太大的亂子……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#11$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少女深深地呼出一口氣，伏倒在桌案上，一直以來挺直如同雪中松柏的腰背終於卸力鬆垮下去。"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我真不明白，為什麼人們總是會將神明當成許願機呢？為什麼要將世上的所有幸運與不幸都歸咎到神明身上呢？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，身為聖女不應該這樣想，可是……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是我也不明白，為什麼偏偏在這種時候會有天災發生……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#7$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雅兒，還是叫換衣的侍從們進來吧。", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "恩雅", "content": "喪禮儀式已經準備就緒，從明日開始，我們就……"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "恩雅", "content": "雅兒？"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drtywndblw", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodcracle", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼喚聲落下，房間中依舊寂靜，唯有風聲與火聲交織。"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅回過頭，她這才發現房間內空無一人。"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雅兒……你在嗎？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#5$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#5$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原本應該時常陪伴在聖女身旁的侍女長消失無蹤，只有恩雅一個人的影子被火光拖得又細又長，在昏暗的房間裡不斷閃爍跳躍。"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雅兒……？", "name": "恩雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_174_slbell_1#6$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.8, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅……", "name": "大長老"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……誠實地告訴我……", "name": "大長老"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還能……聽到耶拉岡德的聲音嗎？", "name": "大長老"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 1.5, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.7, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "67_i03", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3, "y": 50.0, "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"yFrom": 50.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 25.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柴火燃燒的劈啪聲在空蕩蕩的房間內迴響。"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "窗外的風依舊呼嘯，似乎可以聽見聖山之下，迷茫的信眾嚎哭的聲音。"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩雅還記得初次來到這間屬於聖女的房間時的感受。"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陌生的房間，不一樣的氣味，目所能及卻再也不能以自己的名字返回的家，那時候的她也一樣覺得這個房間空蕩如同雪洞。"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是她已經習慣了有一個人在這裡陪伴自己。有一個人可以讓自己毫無顧慮地傾訴心事，可以讓自己有所依賴。"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但此時……"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "翻閱到一半的《耶拉岡德》古老的卷軸鋪在桌面上，梳妝鏡裡映出少女茫然無措的臉。"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雅兒……", "name": "恩雅"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你明明答應過我，不會忽然被帶走的。", "name": "恩雅"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底……到底發生了什麼……", "name": "恩雅"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}